title: Full-stack Developer
mkt-description: Final project of module 3 of the  Programming from Scratch' course at Cubos Academy. On the front-end, React was used with the react-hook-form, react-router-dom, react-use and material-ui libraries. In the back-end, Node was used with the express, bcrypt, json-webtoken, cors, dotenv and pg libraries. The database was PostgreSQL.
cubos-flix-description: Cubos Flix is a fictional website developed at the end of the second module of the Cubos Academy's Programming from scratch course. This website was developed with React using componentization concepts, hooks useState and useEffect, storing information in localStorage.
